[[Image:Logo-vegas.png|right|frame|Las Vegas 2005 Internext Logo]]
'''Internext-Expo''' is a biannual adult industry networking event [[B2B]] and convention for the adult [[Internet]] industry professionals and those who work within the Adult Digital Media and Webmaster Marketplace to connect and do business with others in the industry.{{Fact|date=October 2008}}

Originally entitled IA2000 and owned by Steve Hearne, it was changed to Internext or Internext-Expo in 2001 by its new owners [[AVN_(magazine)]] who took it over in 1998. {{Fact|date=December 2008}}

Internext Winter is usually held in January in Las Vegas at the conclusion of the Adult Entertainment Expo. Internext Summer is usually held in Hollywood, Florida in August.



