'''Pornophobia''' refers to fear of [[pornography]]. It is a common [[phobia]].<ref>[http://www.blifaloo.com/info/phobias.php] Phobia Dictionary</ref> Feminist [[Nadine Strossen]] in her article ''The perils of pornophobia'' published in ''The Humanist'' identified that pornophobia can be seen among pro-censorship feminists and conservatives.<ref>[[Nadine Strossen]], [http://www.thefreelibrary.com/The+perils+of+pornophobia-a016898789 The perils of pornophobia] ''The Humanist''</ref>
