{{About|a sexual slang term|the food item|cream pie}} '''Creampie''', or '''internal [[cum shot]]''',<ref name=Carroll>{{cite book|title=Popular modernity in America: experience, technology, mythohistory|publisher=[[SUNY Press]]|author=Michael Thomas Carroll |year=2000|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=fzSrmR1PRO0C|isbn=0791447138|page=119}}</ref> is a [[slang]] term used in [[pornography]] to describe when a male [[Ejaculation|ejaculates]] inside his partner's [[vagina]] or [[anus]].<ref name=Partridge>{{cite book|title=The New Partridge Dictionary of Slang and Unconventional English: A-I|publisher=[[Taylor & Francis]]|author=Eric Partridge, Tom Dalzell, Terry Victor |year=2006|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=4YfsEgHLjboC|isbn=0415259371|page=507}}</ref> The term 'oral creampie' is used less commonly to refer to ejaculation in the mouth.<ref name=Partridge/> The term also refers to the visible "seeping" or dripping of semen from the aforementioned orifices.<ref name=Carroll/><ref name=Partridge/><ref name=Creed>{{cite book|title=Media matrix: sexing the new reality|publisher=[[Allen & Unwin]]|author=Barbara Creed |year=2003|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=HhMBgOzMUpQC|isbn=1865089265|page=61}}</ref> The word originated in U.S. pornography in the early 2000s.<ref name=Partridge/> In pornography, vaginal sex is generally followed by a [[facial (sexuality)|facial]] or other visible ejaculation; creampies have been called the "counterimage" of facials.<ref name=Carroll/> Ejaculating in the vagina is a rarer situation which can be advertised to attract viewers. The uncommon nature is due to the fact that ejaculating inside the vagina significantly increases the risk of [[pregnancy]] if the actress is not using some form of birth control. Some pornographic films use an artificial semen substitute to create creampie shots.<ref name=Partridge/><ref name=Creed/> Examples of pornographic film series which focus on the act include ''Cream Filled Teens'' and ''Internal Combustion''.<ref name=Kick>{{cite book|title=Disinformation book of lists: subversive facts and hidden information in rapid-fire format|publisher=[[The Disinformation Company]]|author=[[Russ Kick|Russell Kick]] |year=2004|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=utssHzXYsWoC|isbn=0972952942|page=192}}</ref>
==Terms and concepts== ;Creampie eating: When someone eats the semen either by scooping it out with their fingers, performing [[cunnilingus]] or [[anilingus]], or sucking it through a straw or tube; this is often known as [[felching]]. ;Cumfart: Refers to [[farting]] (or squeezing) the semen out of the anus or vagina. Examples include ''Blow it Out Your Ass'' by [[Elegant Angel]], which focuses on milk [[enemas]] and anal creampies. <ref name=Hunter>{{cite web |url=http://www.xbiz.com/articles/82856 |title=Elegant Angel |accessdate=2009-04-11 |author=Hunter, Tod |date=2007-08-10 |work= |publisher=[[XBIZ]]}}</ref> ;Creampie [[gang bang]]: A porn scene in which someone receives multiple creampies from several men. Examples include ''Five Guy Cream Pie''. <ref name=Kick/> ;Oral creampie: When performing [[fellatio]], when reaching climax, the giver ejaculates semen into the receiver's mouth. {{Citation needed|date=September 2009}}
