==Jordan Capri== {{Female adult bio |name= Jordan Capri |photo= |hair color= |natural bust= |ethnicity= |height= |weight= |homepage= http://www.jordancapri.com }}
Name: Jordan Capri Birthplace: San Diego, California Measurements: 5′1″, 107 lbs, 34A-26-36 Started Modeling: 2003
Jordan Capri was discovered in 2003 by photographer Steve Lightspeed, and quickly became a star of the Lightspeed network of sites, including Ls-Sorority.com, LS-University.com, and her own sologirl site, JordanCapri.com. Jordan’s petite body and innocent looks have made her a fan favorite in the “barely-legal” niche. Jordan has been nominated multiple times for “Web Starlet of the Year” as well as winning “Best SoloGirl Site” of 2007. In 2008, Jordan’s website celebrated its 200,000th paying member.
Referred to as “The Queen of Cute”, Jordan has appeared at numerous adult industry trade shows to sign autographs and meet her fans. She has been featured in AVN Online Magazine, The FUBAR Times, Klixxx Magazine, as well as being “Miss January” in the 2009 AVN Calendar.
Jordan is best known for performing with Tawnee Stone in Tawnee’s first-ever lesbian scene, and for her infamous “Honeymoon Hardcore Video” which was leaked onto the web by her ex-husband in 2006. Jordan has guest starred on many other sites, including TaylorLittle.com, TawneeStone.com, and LightspeedGirls.com. She is the star of 18 DVD titles, including “Lightspeed Sorority: Jordan Capri”, and is currently working on several new titles to be released in 2009.
When not on camera, Jordan attends college and enjoys hiking, working out, watching movies, and hanging out with her friends.
