{{Infobox Company | name = Cross | logo = | type = | genre = | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = 2005 | founder = Matsushima Cross | defunct = | location_city = {{flagicon|Japan}} [[Ebisu, Tokyo]] | location_country = [[Japan]] | location = | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = [[Pornography]] | products = [[Pornographic films]] | services = | market cap = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = http://www.crosscross.jp/top.html | footnotes = | intl = }}
{{Nihongo|'''Cross'''|クロス}} is a Japanese [[adult video]] (AV) studio located in Tokyo at the [[Ebisu, Tokyo|Ebisu Garden Place Tower]].
==Company information== Cross was founded by directors Matsushima Cross (松嶋クロス) and Innjean Koga (インジャン古河) in late 2005, the event being announced at a press conference at a club in [[Tokyo]]'s [[Shinjuku]] district on October 19, 2005.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20051130A/|title=時代と発想のＡＶメーカー・クロス参上！|publisher=[http://allabout.co.jp/ AllAbout]|last=Otsubo|first=Kemuta|date=November 30, 2005|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/nlbn/NL000500/vl_32.htm|title=新メーカー・ＣＲＯＳＳ、11.19発進！|publisher=[http://allabout.co.jp/ AllAbout]|last=Otsubo|first=Kemuta|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref> Cross had previously been a director for AV studios [[Kuki Inc.|Kuki]], Max-A and Try-Heart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jans-web.com/profiles/n2119&mode=movies|title=Matsushima Cross 松嶋クロス |publisher=[http://www.jans-web.com/ Urabon Navigator]|accessdate=2009-05-22}}</ref> while Koga had formerly directed for [[V&R Planning]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jans-web.com/profiles/n2686&mode=movies|title=Innjean Koga インジャン古河 |publisher=[http://www.jans-web.com/ Urabon Navigator]|accessdate=2009-05-22}}</ref> The studio's first videos, labeled with the production codes CRPD-001 to CRPD-010, were released on November 19, 2005 and included [[AV Idol]]s [[An Nanba]] and [[Riko Tachibana]] among the actresses.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/works/-/list/=/article=release/date=2005/|title=2005年発売作品一覧 (2005 Production Catalog)|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref> Matsushima Cross announced his retirement from AV and left the company in June 2007.<ref name="spysee">{{cite web|url=http://spysee.jp/%E6%9D%BE%E5%B6%8B%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B9/|title=松嶋クロス (Matsushima Cross)|publisher=[http://spysee.jp/ spysee.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref>
As of June 2009, the studio had released over 300 original videos, an average of about seven videos per month since the studio's origin in 2005. Cross also produces compilation videos using scenes from previous original Cross videos using production codes of the form CRAD-xxx with CRAD-023 coming out in June 2009.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/works/-/list/=/article=release/date=200511/|title=2009年発売作品一覧 (2009 Production Catalog)|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref> Cross distributes its videos for DVD sales and online viewing through the [[Hokuto Corporation]] via their DMM website..<ref name="outvision maker">{{cite web|url=http://www.outvision.co.jp/maker/index.html|title=メーカー一覧を見る|publisher=[http://www.outvision.co.jp/ Outvision]|language=Japanese|accessdate=2008-12-07}}</ref> Yamada Kensuke (山田 健介) is listed as the Manager of Operations for the company.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/privacy.html|title=個人情報保護方針について (Individual Privacy Policy)|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref>
==Directors== In addition to Matsushima Cross, a number of directors, past and present, have also made videos with Cross. The most prominent among them has been Dragon Nishikawa who has directed over 120 videos or more than a third of all Cross productions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/works/-/list/=/article=director/id=3|title=ドラゴン西川監督作品一覧 (Dragon Nishikawa Director Works)|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-24|language=Japanese}}</ref> {| |valign="top" width=50%| *Zack Arai (ザック荒井) *Captain Ehara (キャプテン江原) *Kikurin (菊淋) *Innjean Koga (インジャン古河) *Dragon Nishikawa (ドラゴン西川) *Pinky Osanai (ピンキー小山内) |valign="top" width=22| |valign="top" width=50%| *[[Sakura Sakurada]] (桜田さくら) *Tiger Sakei (タイガー小堺) *Tatsuhito Suzuki (鈴木達仁) *Tomoyasu Takei (武井寅泰) *Shinosuke Takinogawa (滝野川進之助) |}
==Actresses== Among the various prominent [[AV Idol]]s who have performed in Cross videos, probably the one most closely associated with the company has been [[Sakura Sakurada]] who has appeared in 28 Cross videos. Sakurada first starred for Cross in ''Invincibility Molester'' released in March 2006 and has continued acting for the studio through mid-2009. She also made her debut as a director in the Cross video ''The Maniac Lesbians' Filming Party'' from March 2008. She directed a second movie for Cross, ''Big Bust New Faces Lesbian Interview'', in August 2008.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/works/-/list/=/article=actress/id=7581/|title=桜田さくら 出演作品一覧 (Sakura Sakurada Video Catalog)|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref>
Other actresses appearing for Cross include: {| |valign="top" width=50%| *[[Hotaru Akane]] *Chihiro Hara *[[Hikari Hino]] *[[Milk Ichigo]] *MEW |valign="top" width=22| |valign="top" width=50%| *[[Miki Mizuasa]] *[[Ayano Murasaki]] *[[An Nanba]] *[[Riko Tachibana]] *[[Maki Tomoda]] |}
==AV Open== Cross entered the 2007 [[AV Open]] contest in the Challenge division for directors. Cross took the First Place Award with the entry from director Captain Ehara, ''Anal Splash Thick Lesbian United!'' (肛門潮吹き極太合体レズビアン), starring Chihiro Hara, [[Hotaru Akane]] & [[Sakura Sakurada]], labeled OPEN-0755 for the contest and later released as CRPD-209. The video also won the Lily Franky Honorary President Prize at the AV Open<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dmm.co.jp/mono/dvd/avopen/avopen02_result.html|title=2nd AV Open Results|publisher=[http://www.dmm.co.jp/ www.dmm.co.jp]|accessdate=2008-10-02|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crosscross.jp/works/-/detail/=/cid=crpd209/|title=肛門潮吹き極太合体レズビアン|publisher=[http://www.crosscross.jp/ www.crosscross.jp]|accessdate=2009-05-22|language=Japanese}}</ref>
