{{nihongo|'''Wanz Factory'''|ワンズファクトリー}} is a Japanese [[adult video]] production company located in the [[Toshima, Tokyo|Toshima]] ward of [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]].<ref name="about">{{cite web|url=http://www.wanz.jp/aboutus.php|title=会社概要 (About Us)|publisher=[http://www.wanz.jp/ www.wanz.jp]|accessdate=2009-06-06|language=Japanese}}</ref>
==Company information== The company was founded in March 2000 and presently employs 20 people. Their adult videos are sold in more than 3000 stores nationwide in Japan.<ref name="about"/> Japanese adult video studios are usually divided into mainstream and independent types, the mainstream or "pro" studios such as [[Kuki Inc.|Kuki]], [[Alice Japan]] and [[h.m.p. (Japan)|h.m.p]] often being larger and older than the "indie" companies such as [[Soft On Demand]], [[Cross (studio)|Cross]], [[Dogma (studio)|Dogma]] and [[Moodyz]] while the latter usually have less censorship and are more adventurous in their offerings. Wanz Factory is one of the indie companies with a specialty in [[AV Idol]] videos and large-busted "big boobs" models.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://memweb.newsguy.com/~japanav/other/avfaq.html|title=Who makes AV?|publisher=[http://memweb.newsguy.com/~japanav/ Japan AV]|last=Banana Boy|accessdate=2009-03-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.jmate.com/reviews/article_151.html|title=Bad Girl-Ami Ayukawa|publisher=[http://www.jmate.com/ JMate]|last=Leongolo|accessdate=2009-06-06}}</ref> The studio releases about 16-17 videos per month including some 10 new original works.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wanz.jp/kensaku/index.php|title=発売月別検索 (Sale Issues by Month)|publisher=[http://www.wanz.jp/ www.wanz.jp]|accessdate=2009-06-15|language=Japanese}}</ref> The major Japanese video distributor DMM listed 1542 DVD and 383 VHS titles for Wanz Factory in mid-June 2009.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dmm.co.jp/search/=/category=mono/searchstr=wI6VysOMxOedxJSXlv7D3cDZ/analyze=V1EAAFYAUAU_/|title=”ワンズファクトリー”の検索結果 人気順 (Wanz Factory Manufacturer Search)|publisher=[http://www.dmm.co.jp/ www.dmm.co.jp]|accessdate=2009-06-16|language=Japanese}}</ref>
