{{Infobox Company | name = Madonna | logo = | type = | genre = | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = 2003 | founder = | defunct = | location_city = {{flagicon|Japan}}Tokyo | location_country = [[Japan]] | location = | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = [[Pornography]] | products = [[Pornographic films]] | services = | market cap = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = [[Hokuto Corporation]] | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = {{cite web|url=http://www.madonna-av.com/top.html|title=Madonna Official Site}} | footnotes = | intl = }}
{{nihongo|'''Madonna'''|マドンナ|Madonna}} is a Japanese adult video (AV) studio which specializes in the "mature woman" genre of Japanese pornography.
==Company information== Madonna is an AV studio located in [[Tokyo]]<ref name="help">{{cite web|url=https://www.madonna-av.com/help/help.html|title=Madonna Help|publisher=[https://www.madonna-av.com/ www.madonna-av.com]|language=Japanese|accessdate=2009-08-11}}</ref> which is affiliated with the large AV conglomerate [[Hokuto Corporation]] which distributes its videos through the DMM website.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.outvision.co.jp/maker/index.html|title=メーカー一覧を見る|publisher=[http://www.outvision.co.jp/ Outvision]|language=Japanese|accessdate=2008-12-07}}</ref> Madonna registered its website www.madonna-av.com in October 2003<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/madonna-av.com|title=madonna-av.com|publisher=[http://www.alexa.com/ Alexa]|accessdate=2009-08-11}}</ref> and released its first videos in December 2003.<ref name="release">{{cite web|url=http://www.madonna-av.com/works/-/release/|title=Madonna Release Day|publisher=[https://www.madonna-av.com/ www.madonna-av.com]|language=Japanese|accessdate=2009-08-11}}</ref> The company specializes in movies in the {{nihongo|"mature woman"|熟女}} or "jukujo" genre, sometimes with an incest theme.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/subject/msubsub_indiesav4.htm|title=自主規制のＡＶメーカー（ま・や行）|publisher=[http://allabout.co.jp/ All About]|last=Otsubo|first=Kemuta|accessdate=2009-08-11|language=Japanese}}</ref> Such mature woman videos have been a growing trend in Japanese AV since the mid 1990s.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://xxx.xcity.jp/SHIN-TOHO/HISTORY/S_SHINOZAKI/index.html|title=Satomi Shinozaki biography|accessdate=2009-08-11|publisher=[http://xxx.xcity.jp/SHIN-TOHO/HISTORY/ Shin-Toho History]|quote=since the middle of '90s when mature women started getting popular in porn movies.}}</ref> The General Manager of the company is {{nihongo|Katsuhisa Aoyagi|青柳勝久}}.<ref name="help"/>
Since their inception, the studio's original videos used production codes series of the type JUK-001 for VHS releases and JUKD-001 for DVD releases. Compilation videos were labeled in the series JUS-001 and JUSD-001. In December 2008, the original code was filled when video JUKD-999 was released. A new series of codes for DVDs was inaugurated in January 2009 in the format JUC-001. Compilation videos are still using the JUSD-xxx format. The studio produces a total of about 20 original and compilation videos per month.<ref name="release"/> As an addition to the standard Madonna label, in November 2007, Madonna instituted a new label, Fitch, which uses codes of the type JUFD-001.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://jans-web.com/?p=maker&maker_id=71&label_id=389|title=Maker: Madonna Label:Fitch|accessdate=2009-08-11|publisher=[http://jans-web.com/ Urabon Navigator]}}</ref>
==AV Grand Prix== Madonna entered the 2008 [[AV Grand Prix]] competition with the 3-hour video ''MADONNA BOOTCAMP ELITE'' [AVGL-025] starring Ryoko Murakami, Chisato Shouda, Sayaka Kawase, Rina Uozumi, Mami Todo, Asami Kitamura, Shino Kodama and Rie Sato.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dmm.co.jp/avgp/sp/gp_list.html|title=AV Grand Prix 2008 Grand Prix Stage|publisher=[http://www.dmm.co.jp/ www.dmm.co.jp]|accessdate=2008-10-05|language=Japanese}}</ref> In the 2009 AV Grand Prix, the Madonna entry ''Raped Female Teacher'' (犯された女教師) [AVGL-136] starring Reiko Makihara and directed by Eitaro Haga won one of the Special Awards for Mature Woman Videos.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.av-gp.com/news/avgp_result/bottom.html|title=AVGP 2009 Result announcement|publisher=[http://www.av-gp.com/ www.av-gp.com]|accessdate=2009-03-02|language=Japanese}}</ref>
