[[ja:マドンナ (アダルトビデオ)]]

A '''{{nihongo|pink salon|ピンクサロン|pinkusaron}}''', or '''{{nihongo|pinsaro|ピンサロ|}}''' for short, is a type of [[brothel]] in [[Japan]] which specialises in [[oral sex]]. 

A pink salon is unusual in that the service is offered in small booths within a large open-plan room. The client is served [[soft drink]]s or [[alcoholic beverage]]s by the "companion" who performs [[fellatio]] on him. There may also be additional activities such as [[Fingering (sexual act)|fingering]] the "companion" and [[sumata]].


