{{nihongo|'''Marina Matsushima'''|松嶋まりな|Matsushima Marina|extra=born [[December 24]], [[1980]]}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] adult film actress and [[AV idol]] famous for her large J cup (DD cup in American measurements) natural [[breasts]].

==Life and career==
Matsushima was scouted from her OL ([[office lady]]) job by a talent scout for adult films. She has supposedly forsaken [[brassiere|bra]]s because they are essentially unavailable in her size in Japan. She has released many movies that focus on her large breasts.

Her first AV was the March 2001 release, {{nihongo|''Enormous Breasts DNA''|爆乳 DNA|Bakyunyu DNA}}, for the [[Crystal-Eizou]] company's Grace label.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://homepage3.nifty.com/kurokami/years/years_2001.htm|title=2001|accessdate=2007-07-21|publisher=[http://homepage3.nifty.com/kurokami/index.html AV {{nihongo2|研究所}} (AV Research Laboratory)]}}</ref> She was featured in the May, 2004 omnibus collection from TMA, ''The Charismatic Idol BEST COLLECTION'' with fellow big-bust [[AV idol]], [[Kyoko Ayana]]. The video focused on a variety of styles of sex.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vinfo.xcity.jp/english/info.html?ID=TWV082|title=''The Charismatic Idol BEST COLLECTION''|accessdate=2007-04-28|work=[http://avidol.xcity.jp/english/index.html AV Idol Directory]|language=English}}</ref> Matsushima has done several [[breast fetishism|fetish]] photobooks and videos in the [[Bondage (BDSM)|bondage]] genre. Her later performances depict her as the aggressor, dominating her male co-stars. Japanese [http://www.amazon.co.jp/s?__mk_ja_JP=%83J%83%5E%83J%83i&url=search-alias%3Daps&field-keywords=%8F%BC%93%88%82%DC%82%E8%82%C8 Amazon] shows 25 DVDs, 13 VHS tapes and 6 photo-books featuring Marina Matsuhima currently available. 

The [[Tokyo Topless]] website, which has been in existence since March 1995, and claims to be the first adult site in Asia has devoted two photo features to Marina Matsushima with photographer Seiji Okamura.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tokyotopless.com/model/MarinaMATSUSHIMA/01/|title=Marina MATSUSHIMA 01|accessdate=2007-06-09|work=tokyotopless.com|language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tokyotopless.com/model/MarinaMATSUSHIMA/02/|title=Marina MATSUSHIMA 02|accessdate=2007-06-09|work=tokyotopless.com|language=Japanese}}</ref> The July, 2004 release of her DVD ''Fetish Diva'' gave her a third feature at the site, this time photographed by Koji Yokoyama.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tokyotopless.com/model/MarinaMATSUSHIMA/03/|title=Marina MATSUSHIMA 03|accessdate=2007-06-09|work=tokyotopless.com|language=Japanese}}</ref>

