{{nihongo|'''Nishimura Rika'''|西村理香|extra=born 1981}} is a nude [[gravure idol]] of [[Japan]] promoted by photographer {{nihongo|[[Rikitake Yasushi| Rikitake Yasushi]]|[[:ja:力武靖|力武靖]]}} who, even to this day enjoys the status of a legend and great popularity. Her real name is unknown. 

Beginning from 1994 to 1999, she released nude [[photobook]]s and videos, among which were two volumes of the famous photobook series FRIENDS by [[Rikitake Yasushi]]. The year 2004 saw the reprinting of "Pretty Girl of Legend - Nishimura Rika" in May and, in December, the release of a DVD compilation entitled "Rika, 22 years old - A goddess reincarnated". 

In violation of [[intellectual property]] law, her photography is often spread over the Internet, appearing under names such as Ding, Eri, Erika, Fizuka, Fumie, Fumiko.

