'''Hanako Nanjô''' (なんじょうはなこ/楠城華子/''Nanjô Hanako''). (Born in [[Shimonoseki, Yamaguchi]], Japan, in [[April 2, 1980]]) is a Japanese actress, singer, model and gravure idol. She's moved from Shimonoseki, Yamaguchi to Tokyo, Japan at 12 and studied at [[Tokyo University]]. She burst on to the scene in 2005 and has several DVDs, photobooks and television appearances. Spelled Hanako Nanjo as well.
